               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Mazmur, Antiphones for Sundays of the year (fols. 3ra-32rb)
 II)
                     Dǝggʷā, Antiphonary (from the feast of St John the Baptist to the vigil of the
                     feast of Qʷǝsqʷam, 5th of Ḫǝdār) (fols. 32ra-130ra) 
 
 Additio
                     1.</summary>
